ai-patthana23.39:0.2_0: under the investigation of principles means to the extent of the Dhamma.
ai-patthana23.39:1.1_0: Not is principle not skilled in means of not wearing shame, nor doing what is skillful.
ai-patthana23.39:1.1_1: One doesn’t give rise to unprofitable things, so skilled in means of repulsion.
ai-patthana23.39:1.1_2: Not is skilled in loss of impingement and not doing anywhere. And this is not skillful, blameless, and what is unskillful.
ai-patthana23.39:1.1_4: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
ai-patthana23.39:2.1_0: Not being exerted, not skilled in loss of focusing on skillfulness, not countering repulsion regarding what is unskillful.
ai-patthana23.39:2.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
ai-patthana23.39:3.1_0: Not in needing, or in fact, or inspires confidence in those without it. ...
ai-patthana23.39:3.1_1: This is the section in brief.
ai-patthana23.39:4.1_0: In the Nerañjarā, which is the incomparable recommendation? What is the plane of spears less than twenty-two years.
